minijava.typecheck.symboltable
类 ClassTable

java.lang.Object
  minijava.typecheck.symboltable.SymbolTable
      minijava.typecheck.symboltable.ClassTable

public class ClassTable
extends SymbolTable

Identified by class name. Usage: Insert and find attributes and methods of this class.
Used via "(any instance of SymbolTable).globalTable.getClassTable(this class name)" (Recommended)

作者：
ZongZiWang
